{"tid":1352034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家好多人出post散播白色恐怖叫人唔好去727光復元朗","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:18:32.000Z","uid":73143,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c3b5434f716670039b5c74ad84c13c20422d4d0","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:14:54.000Z","msg":"我唔知佢地咩心態，但727光復元朗係日後和理非出唔出黎既一個關鍵<br />\n如果你地連咁樣比人蝦到上心口都唔敢行出黎<br />\n咁之後仲邊會仲有和理非肯出黎一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無人可以咁樣搞香港人"},{"pid":"a6958754fc9a7ac947f138e224c1ce8e6d284568","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b03c793eeeade465e773fe1d959dc2f6fda1cc","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1909776146672216ee5da1ffd9a098daa818b6f3","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a49b1ddc8c600cb622d3083ca9228ea6cadf223","tid":1352034,"uid":59989,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:17:46.000Z","msg":"俾恰到上心口<br />\n你人多驚條撚咩<br />\n真係唔店咪be water一齊走<br />\n連威都唔示下 仲得了？<br />\n每次遊行完 佢地揀一區斬都得呀"},{"pid":"cfa9015780cb6895db80027d7da8a3902b9ff29d","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7e1dd18cf7c0f6cc1d1c6b0a36ca1a6adff783","tid":1352034,"uid":248384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"驚都未撚驚過 愈講得恐怖愈想去 <br />\n麻煩當日準備定戰鼓"},{"pid":"38a2abd8b4e4bfe2035da425fa95373ad1fc9c37","tid":1352034,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:19:30.000Z","msg":"From Simon Lui (Facebook)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156060495911105%26set%3Da.45435071104%26type%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=178d1f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n我經歷過波士頓馬拉松爆炸案，明白襲擊後的恐怖<br />\n1) 爆炸前30分鐘，我仍在Boylston st現場，只是早走了<br />\n2) MIT校警就在我Lab樓下(Building 32)被槍殺，只是我偷懶無返工(偷懶萬歲)<br />\n<br />\n我嗰晚好驚，本來諗住「一星期唔出街，以後見人都要提防」... 但原來我錯了<br />\n<br />\n【恐佈分子的目的，不是要讓100人死掉，而是要令幾億人害怕】<br />\n<br />\n是波士頓人教曉我，面對恐懼就要更勇敢。因為爆炸後第二晚，波士頓人竟然這樣：<br />\n- 不躲在家中，照常出街跑步<br />\n- 不讓恐懼擴散，反而故意外出食飯購物<br />\n- 人與人之間的信任沒有動搖。反而整網頁讓居民登記，開放自己家，讓因爆炸案錯過火車的旅人住一晚 <br />\n<br />\n「開放自己家！黐線㗎！引狼入室！」不是的<br />\n- 若恐佈分子要襲擊，點會無方法？<br />\n- 由華盛頓來旅行但錯過火車嘅自己人，點會睇唔出？幫佢點會有事？<br />\n- 自己人互相幫助，其實安全得很<br />\n- 所以最後，我自己都踩單車出去飲咖啡，重買水比站崗嘅人<br />\n<br />\n恐佈分子的失敗，在於居民鎮定不害怕，在於鄰里關係沒有動搖。若要防範恐佈分子，不是要人人自危，而是要把問題源頭清掉吧。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，守望相助，不要落單，齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9058c1090a626cf09f2bdb682d5189e7a50c6a","tid":1352034,"uid":174752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"如果係真心叫人唔好去，咁果班人其實冇人性，自己&ldquo;同路人&rdquo;比人打到仆街都可以好&ldquo;冷靜&rdquo;叫人以&ldquo;大局為重&rdquo;,依種人連垃圾都唔係，枉稱為人"},{"pid":"5a359237cabab1952a320c5086dde745fa272a47","tid":1352034,"uid":52566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaF2AaN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaF2AaN.png&h=f1c1d386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4c98c85a4c82ec4ee7f62d986af7e2344a7509c","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3286572eeeea79689a1ee3544c031c7199740b3","tid":1352034,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:31:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"469b3b947a09794259cfd26fbbf1de2ac4ee0b55","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:37:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a396690b4a41e245fa39a282365cf1f367f36bf1","tid":1352034,"uid":263806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:05.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔可以搞<br />\n但人地出刀 你唔可以淨係出遮<br />\n要有最壞打算<br />\n要有最好防護同攻擊力<br />\n佢哋要劈友 唔會留力 全部刀手都用錢買返嚟唔會留力"},{"pid":"30a54af8aa79de7ebb740cdbd67806314eb5753f","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3628c864a5885a1fa9cc190dea031d7b5663ff2","tid":1352034,"uid":43082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"我地一定要去元朗！<br />\n<br />\n如果少人就更加多市民受傷<br />\n<br />\n人多就係保護我地既最大武器！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"3f48c5fe8384690c6331b8a2edeee65f443e5bd3","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:06:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24593d3bebcd689414386031178c6d48ebe3a03f","tid":1352034,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06369b3df0591f54b094528fc37916632e1fec47","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152fbf4067d9aee83988448d35b4d75cee7f1764","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0dda1549938dcf24adb6846d16c8a77ba6cb62","tid":1352034,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef57c56b7d1e66504d0ed4a5b5348468ddfb5d69","tid":1352034,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}